title: Jimmy Scott - The Savoy Years & More (1955-1975) 3 CD
description:
LITTLE JIMMY SCOTT _ THE SAVOY YEARS AND MORE

This deluxe three CD box set covers all the Roost sessions they could find, which is only one Roost session, but it is a good one and it has Budd Johnson, Charles Mingus And Mundell Lowe among others. It is from 1955. Then we have the complete Savoy recordings, which were done between 1955 and 1960. The final session on this magnificent collection was recorded in 1975 and was originally issued by Savoy. More details are provided in the booklet which I have thoughtfully scanned and included in this "must seed" torrent which is more than qualified to be passed down through the ages, or failing that, to perhaps be discovered and appreciated by some more worthy extraterrestrial life form.
